{"word":"συγχαίρω","slug":"συγχαίρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συγχαίρω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:χαίρω\">χαίρω</a></el>] ‘have joy in association with’, <b>rejoice<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on sharing another’s joy <b><a href='B:490 1:58'>Lk 1:58</a>; <a href='B:490 15:6'>15:6</a>, <a href='B:490 15:9'>9</a>; <a href='B:530 12:26'>1 Cor 12:26</a>; <a href='B:570 2:17'>Phil 2:17f</a>.</b> Some favor the rendering congratulate for <el>σ.</el> in <b><a href='B:490 1:58'>Lk 1:58</a>; <a href='B:570 2:17'>Phil 2:17f</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> that causes joy: truth <b><a href='B:530 13:6'>1 Cor 13:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συγκυρία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συγχάρητε\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}